itemDisplayName: Deploy a 5 Node Windows Service Fabric Cluster with NSG enabled
description: This template allows you to deploy a secure 5 node Service Fabric Cluster running Windows Server 2019 Datacenter on a Standard_D2_V2 Size VMSS, with network security groups enabled.
summary: This template takes a minimum amount of parameters and deploys 5 Node Service Fabric Cluster running windows with NSG enabled
